{"tid":122071,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"有無用緊onkyo e700bt嘅巴打麻煩入一入黎","createTime":"2017-02-15T17:41:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-17T11:20:41.000Z","uid":52934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"68a3c8ba5b2f8c9ebcc33aaaf4a457e1e0da134d","tid":122071,"uid":52934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T17:41:01.000Z","msg":"我自己用緊mbp+6s+aw2<br />\n琴日第一日用個headphone, 部mbp一開始detect唔到<br />\n搞左一大輪終於得, 試睇youtube delay到傻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跟手諗住試吓用部iPhone connect, bluetooth完全search唔到, 錶入邊個藍牙都搵唔到, 究竟個connection真係咁廢定係純粹我個隻係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a49c45ad7710167a525736a8831cfa102659d9a","tid":122071,"uid":5025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T17:42:05.000Z","msg":"冇用過哩隻<br />\n但會唔會係淨係可以pair 1部device?"},{"pid":"f95537546341d3517660767de0b13fdfae7edc09","tid":122071,"uid":52934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T17:44:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇用過哩隻<br />\n但會唔會係淨係可以pair 1部device?</blockquote><br />\n唔該巴打先，不過佢有個function係多重配對，應該就唔會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cbae58d78221edb79eecdf9af85f9a92a452110","tid":122071,"uid":39601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T23:45:03.000Z","msg":"Pair係要長按開關直到LED藍白燈咁閃下閃下<br />\n我用緊, 連接到Vaio Laptop, Android, 無delay<br />\niphone<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  nfc 又block左, 又唔可以用nfc connect"},{"pid":"a61dcec3217044ad94d535118d815c1f6cebf614","tid":122071,"uid":52934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T01:52:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Pair係要長按開關直到LED藍白燈咁閃下閃下<br />\n我用緊, 連接到Vaio Laptop, Android, 無delay<br />\niphone<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  nfc 又block左, 又唔可以用nfc connect</blockquote><br />\n巴打意思即係pair要㩒住粒電源制長過就咁開關?"},{"pid":"c2fbe77f50d1956d3c2d9ddf99e269b